# error handling
# 1. cannot find module 'react-router-dom' --> install it in root
# 2. Error: Can't resolve './pages/AboutPage' in '/home/kali/Downloads/simzmakerover/src' ---------> correct the path in App.js for import and route. 
# 3. Error: export 'Switch' (imported as 'Switch') was not found in 'react-router-dom' ----> replace switch with router or routes in app.js
# 4. Can't resolve '/path-to-your-background-image.jpg' in '/home/kali/Downloads/simzmakerover/src/pages/Home' --------> add image in /assets/images and set path in Home.css 
# 5. Routes is not defined ---------> 


